dt: {bc}a red-fruited upright-growing dewberry ({it}Rubus loganobaccus{/it}) usually regarded as a hybrid of a western dewberry and a red raspberry or sometimes as a variety ({it}R. ursinus loganobaccus{/it}) of a western dewberry

shortdef: a red-fruited upright-growing dewberry (Rubus loganobaccus) usually regarded as a hybrid of a western dewberry and a red raspberry or sometimes as a variety (R. ursinus loganobaccus) of a western dewberry; also : its berry
